I'm Azim Hashim Premji, an Indian business tycoon, investor, and
philanthropist. I am the chairman of Wipro Limited. I have donated 25
percent of my personal wealth to charity. And I also promised to give
away the remaining 25% this year in 2021. I have decided to donate
$2,000,000.00 to you. If you are interested in my donation, please
contact me for more information. I would also like you to become part
of my charity foundation as soon as you receive this money so that we
can use our hands for those in need. You can also learn more about me
by using the link below to read

http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Azim_Premji

Contact by email for more details: azimnhashimpremji@gmail.com

regards
CEO Wipro Limited
Azim Hashim Premji
